        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–9. Telostholus kubani sp. nov., ♂ (1–8, paratype; 9, holotype). 1 and 2, habitus (1, in lateral view; 2, in dorsal view). 3, head in frontal view. 4, head and pronotum in lateral view. 5, head and pronotum in dorsal view. 6, mesosoma part. and T1 in dorso-lateral view. 7, fore wing. 8, hind wing. 9, genitalia in ventral view. Scale bar: 1.0 mm for 1, 2; 0.5 mm for 7, 8; 0.2 mm for 3–6; 0.1 mm for 9." ;
